Package com.suganya.reports

Class FrameworkLogger

java.lang.Object
com.suganya.reports.FrameworkLogger
public final class FrameworkLogger extends Object
Logger class using Consumer Interface feature of Java 8 to log the status to Extent Test in Extent Report
Author:
Suganya Jothiramalingam
